    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Assess for distal pulse, motor, and sensation\nInspect skin for signs of open fracture\nX-ray femur",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
      "links": []
    },
    "Management": {
      "text": "Ortho consult in ED\nIn general, femur fractures in children >6mo require surgical repair",
